{"id":"orch-go-0c0f","title":"Add kb reflect --type open to surface investigations with unimplemented recommendations","description":"kb reflect currently finds clusters by topic prefix but misses open action items.\n\n**Problem:** Investigations with actionable 'Next:' recommendations get buried. Example: FAILURE_REPORT.md template recommended in inv-failure-mode-artifacts but never implemented.\n\n**Solution:** Add --type open mode that:\n1. Finds investigations where Status ≠ Complete  \n2. Extracts the 'Next:' field\n3. Filters out close/none/complete/implemented\n4. Shows what's actionable\n\n**Why not LLM:** D.E.K.N. structure already standardizes where recommendations live. Pattern matching on Next: field is fast, free, and deterministic. Template is the forcing function.\n\n**Test:** rg '\\*\\*Next:\\*\\*' .kb/investigations/*.md | grep -vi 'close|none|complete|implemented'\nCurrently returns 18 open items that kb reflect doesn't surface.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-21T23:19:50.892308-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-21T23:21:18.911397-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-21T23:21:18.911397-08:00"}
