{"id":"orch-go-0sp4","title":"Cross-project agents show as unsynced in dashboard","description":"Agents spawned with --workdir to different project show 'Waiting for activity...' in dashboard because: 1) Workspace is in target project's .orch/workspace/, not current project 2) Beads ID prefix (snap-*) doesn't exist in current project's .beads/ 3) Dashboard can't resolve phase/status across project boundaries. Need to either: a) Track cross-project workspace locations, or b) Query target project's beads, or c) Show helpful 'cross-project' indicator instead of broken state.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-26T09:46:46.307582-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-26T09:54:21.994419-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-26T09:54:21.994419-08:00","close_reason":"Designed multi-project workspace aggregation for cross-project agent visibility. Uses OpenCode session directories for dynamic project discovery. Investigation created with full implementation recommendations. Added feat-017 to features.json.","labels":["skill:systematic-debugging","triage:ready"]}
