{"id":"orch-go-103i","title":"SYNTHESIS model field should come from session metadata, not agent self-report","description":"Agents self-report their model in SYNTHESIS.md Session Metadata section. This is unreliable - agents can hallucinate. Should pull model from OpenCode logs/session metadata (verified: ~/.local/share/opencode/log/ shows actual modelID per request). Either inject correct model into SPAWN_CONTEXT or verify/overwrite during orch complete.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2025-12-30T17:44:07.599471-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-02T13:55:30.120639-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-02T13:55:30.120639-08:00","close_reason":"Fixed SYNTHESIS model to use OpenCode session metadata. Added GetSessionModel helper, tests pass."}
