{"id":"orch-go-1f02","title":"Consolidate session-context.js and orch-session-autostart.ts into single plugin","description":"## Problem\n\nTwo separate OpenCode plugins with overlapping concerns:\n\n| Plugin | Purpose | Event |\n|--------|---------|-------|\n| session-context.js | Loads orchestrator skill | config hook |\n| orch-session-autostart.ts | Runs orch session start | session.created |\n\nBoth:\n- Detect workers (same logic, duplicated)\n- Run at session start\n- Are orchestrator-specific\n- Live in ~/.config/opencode/plugin/\n\n## Why Consolidate\n\n1. **DRY** - isWorker() logic duplicated across both files\n2. **Consistency** - Same detection should use same code\n3. **Maintenance** - Single point of change for orchestrator session setup\n4. **Clarity** - One 'orchestrator session plugin' vs two partial plugins\n\n## Proposed Solution\n\nCreate single `orchestrator-session.ts` plugin that:\n1. Uses `config` hook to inject orchestrator skill (from session-context.js)\n2. Uses `session.created` to auto-start orch session (from orch-session-autostart.ts)\n3. Shares isWorker() detection logic\n4. Removes the two old plugins\n\n## Implementation\n\n```typescript\nexport const OrchestratorSessionPlugin: Plugin = async ({ directory, $ }) =\u003e {\n  // Shared worker detection\n  const worker = await isWorker(directory)\n  \n  return {\n    config: async (config) =\u003e {\n      if (worker) return\n      // Inject orchestrator skill\n      config.instructions.push(skillPath)\n    },\n    event: async ({ event }) =\u003e {\n      if (event.type !== 'session.created') return\n      if (worker) return\n      // Auto-start orch session\n      await $\\`orch session start\\`\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] Single orchestrator-session.ts plugin created\n- [ ] session-context.js removed\n- [ ] orch-session-autostart.ts removed\n- [ ] Both behaviors preserved (skill injection + session auto-start)\n- [ ] Worker detection shared, not duplicated\n\n## References\n\n- ~/.config/opencode/plugin/session-context.js\n- ~/.config/opencode/plugin/orch-session-autostart.ts\n- .kb/investigations/2025-12-29-inv-create-opencode-plugin-orch-session.md","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-29T13:12:27.010076-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-29T13:24:43.185645-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-29T13:24:43.185645-08:00","close_reason":"Consolidated session-context.js and orch-session-autostart.ts into single orchestrator-session.ts plugin at ~/.config/opencode/plugin/. Shared isWorker() detection cached at init, both config (skill injection) and event (session auto-start) hooks preserved. Investigation files updated with lineage. Leave it Better: kn command not available, but learning noted in investigation history (cache detection at init for efficiency)."}
