{"id":"orch-go-20952.4","title":"Phase 3: Port metadata from headers (x-opencode-env-*)","description":"Feature 4 from porting map. Read x-opencode-env-ORCH_WORKER header to set role:worker. Depends on Phase 2. Low complexity.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T14:34:55.496918-08:00","created_by":"dylanconlin","updated_at":"2026-01-27T15:53:24.07252-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-27T15:53:24.07252-08:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"orch-go-20952.4","depends_on_id":"orch-go-20952","type":"parent-child","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"}]}
