{"id":"orch-go-20992","title":"Verify coaching plugin worker detection after OpenCode restart - spawn should generate zero coaching metrics","description":"Quick verification: 1) Note current coaching-metrics.jsonl line count, 2) Perform 5+ tool calls (reads, bash), 3) Check metrics file - this worker session ID should have ZERO entries. If metrics appear for this session, the fix didn't deploy correctly.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-28T11:46:40.366329-08:00","created_by":"dylanconlin","updated_at":"2026-01-28T12:03:28.677563-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-28T12:03:28.677563-08:00","labels":["triage:ready"]}
