{"id":"orch-go-20999","title":"Extend orch doctor to verify all ecosystem binaries","description":"Extend 'orch doctor --stale-only' to check all Dylan CLIs: orch, kb, glass, skillc, agentlog. Consume 'version --json' output from each, compare git_hash to repo HEAD. Report which binaries are stale. Depends on glass and agentlog having version commands.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-28T13:16:46.599703-08:00","created_by":"dylanconlin","updated_at":"2026-01-28T13:30:04.339599-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-28T13:30:04.339599-08:00","labels":["triage:ready"],"comments":[{"id":1,"issue_id":"orch-go-20999","author":"dylanconlin","text":"Scope: 1. Extend orch doctor --stale-only to check all Dylan CLIs (orch, kb, glass, skillc, agentlog) 2. Consume version --json output from each binary 3. Compare git_hash to repo HEAD 4. Report which binaries are stale 5. Verify glass and agentlog have version commands","created_at":"2026-01-28T13:25:58.090066-08:00"},{"id":2,"issue_id":"orch-go-20999","author":"dylanconlin","text":"Phase: Planning - Analyzing current orch doctor implementation and version command structure","created_at":"2026-01-28T13:25:59.287213-08:00"},{"id":3,"issue_id":"orch-go-20999","author":"dylanconlin","text":"Phase: Implementation - Adding --json flag to orch version, then extending doctor to check all ecosystem binaries","created_at":"2026-01-28T13:26:27.853501-08:00"},{"id":4,"issue_id":"orch-go-20999","author":"dylanconlin","text":"Phase: Complete - Extended orch doctor --stale-only to check all ecosystem binaries (orch, kb, glass, skillc, agentlog). Added --json flag to orch version. Binaries without --json support show 'not supported' message. Committed dd4e7150.","created_at":"2026-01-28T13:29:45.090239-08:00"}]}
{"id":"orch-go-20gms","title":"Synthesize tmux investigations (12)","description":"## Synthesis Needed\n\nTopic **tmux** has accumulated 12 investigations that may benefit from consolidation.\n\n### Investigations to synthesize:\n\n- 2025-12-20-inv-migrate-orch-go-tmux-http.md\n- 2025-12-20-inv-tmux-concurrent-delta.md\n- 2025-12-20-inv-tmux-concurrent-epsilon.md\n- 2025-12-20-inv-tmux-concurrent-zeta.md\n- 2025-12-21-debug-orch-send-fails-silently-tmux.md\n- 2025-12-21-inv-add-tmux-fallback-orch-status.md\n- 2025-12-21-inv-add-tmux-flag-orch-spawn.md\n- 2025-12-21-inv-implement-attach-mode-tmux-spawn.md\n- 2025-12-21-inv-tmux-spawn-killed.md\n- 2025-12-22-debug-orch-send-fails-silently-tmux.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-tmux-session-naming-confusing-hard.md\n- 2025-12-23-inv-test-tmux-spawn.md\n\n### Chronicle Timeline\n\n```\n2025-12-19 [INV] CLI orch complete Command Implementation\n2025-12-19 [INV] Set beads issue status to in_progress on spawn\n2025-12-19 [INV] say hello and exit immediately\n2025-12-20 [INV] Add Abandon Command to orch-go\n2025-12-20 [INV] orch-go Add Question Command\n... (run kb chronicle for full timeline)\n```\n\n### Suggested Action\n\n1. Run `kb chronicle \"tmux\"` to understand evolution\n2. Identify patterns and contradictions across investigations\n3. Create a synthesized decision or consolidated investigation\n","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-07T21:14:38.118953-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-07T22:46:58.711426-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-07T22:46:58.711426-08:00","close_reason":"Bulk close: kb reflect synthesis noise","labels":["triage:review"]}
