{"id":"orch-go-27ts","title":"Recent section has same jostling issue as Active - needs stable sort","description":"## Problem\n\nRecent section agents jostle for position as they update, same issue that was fixed for Active section.\n\n## Root Cause\n\nActive section fix (commit c6b9483) changed sort from updated_at to spawned_at for stability. Same fix needed for Recent section.\n\n## Fix\n\nApply same stable sort (spawned_at) to Recent section sorting logic.\n\n## Files\n- web/src/routes/+page.svelte - Recent section sort","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2025-12-24T14:55:37.531457-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-26T12:36:02.650007-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-26T12:36:02.650007-08:00","close_reason":"Fixed Recent section jostling by using spawned_at for stable sort like Active section. Changed sortedRecentAgents to use true instead of false for useStableSort parameter. Commit: dfd61e0"}
