{"id":"orch-go-2fddu","title":"Add crash telemetry to OpenCode fork","description":"## Problem\n\nOpenCode server crashes silently - no logs exist to diagnose root cause. Investigation orch-go-r0s4m confirmed 5+ crashes but couldn't determine why.\n\n## Implementation\n\nAdd to `~/Documents/personal/opencode/packages/opencode/src/server/server.ts`:\n\n```javascript\nprocess.on('uncaughtException', (err) =\u003e {\n  const crash = {\n    timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),\n    type: 'uncaughtException',\n    error: err.message,\n    stack: err.stack,\n    memory: process.memoryUsage()\n  };\n  fs.appendFileSync(\n    path.join(os.homedir(), '.local/share/opencode/crash.log'),\n    JSON.stringify(crash) + '\\n'\n  );\n  process.exit(1);\n});\n\nprocess.on('unhandledRejection', (reason, promise) =\u003e {\n  const crash = {\n    timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),\n    type: 'unhandledRejection',\n    reason: String(reason),\n    memory: process.memoryUsage()\n  };\n  fs.appendFileSync(\n    path.join(os.homedir(), '.local/share/opencode/crash.log'),\n    JSON.stringify(crash) + '\\n'\n  );\n  process.exit(1);\n});\n```\n\n## After Implementation\n\n1. Rebuild: `cd ~/Documents/personal/opencode/packages/opencode \u0026\u0026 bun run build`\n2. Restart: `orch-dashboard restart`\n3. Next crash will produce log entry in `~/.local/share/opencode/crash.log`\n\n## Success Criteria\n\n- Crash log created on next OpenCode crash\n- Log includes error, stack trace, and memory stats\n- Can diagnose actual root cause from log\n\n## Reference\n\n- Investigation: `.kb/investigations/2026-01-23-inv-opencode-server-crashes-under-load.md`","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-23T15:20:31.289893-08:00","created_by":"dylanconlin","updated_at":"2026-01-23T16:48:06.268885-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-23T16:48:06.268885-08:00","close_reason":"Already implemented - needs binary rebuild","labels":["triage:ready"]}
