{"id":"orch-go-2fsl","title":"Active agent titles sometimes unhelpful (e.g. 'Orchestrator skill says')","description":"## Problem\n\nActive agent cards show titles that aren't meaningful. Example: 'Orchestrator skill says' doesn't tell the user what the agent is actually doing.\n\n## Evidence\n\nScreenshot shows an active agent with title 'Orchestrator skill says' - this is the start of the task description but truncated unhelpfully.\n\n## Root Cause\n\nTitle is derived from task description which may start with context rather than the actual task. For investigations spawned with questions, the question text becomes the title.\n\n## Expected\n\nShow a more useful title:\n- Use beads issue title if available\n- Fall back to skill + short task summary\n- Consider extracting the actual task from longer descriptions\n\n## Files\n- web/src/routes/+page.svelte - AgentCard title display\n- cmd/orch/serve.go - agent data sent to UI","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2025-12-24T14:23:43.78697-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-24T14:32:26.608638-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-24T14:32:26.608638-08:00","close_reason":"Added collapsed section preview showing agent task summaries. When sections are collapsed, header now displays first 1-2 agent tasks with +N suffix. All tests pass, commit 185e07b."}
{"id":"orch-go-2fut9","title":"orch frontier CLI command","description":"Core CLI command that displays decidability state in readable format.\n\n**Output:**\n```\nREADY TO RELEASE (3)\n   orch-go-brit3, orch-go-ag261, orch-go-8ke18\n\nBLOCKED - would unblock most first (2)\n   orch-go-ajxm1 → unblocks: orch-go-kz7zr (epic)\n   orch-go-5ubkd → unblocks: orch-go-epx0r, orch-go-q2bp2...\n\nACTIVE (2)\n   orch-go-epx0r [12m]  orch-go-5bpcc [8m]\n```\n\n**Data sources:**\n- Ready: `bd ready` logic\n- Blocked + unblock calculation: dependency traversal\n- Active: agent registry\n\n**Key insight:** Grouped by \"who needs to act\", not by issue type. Readable first, graphical second.\n\n**Provenance:** Discussion 2026-01-24 - realized Cytoscape graph didn't match vision. Wanted scannable text that answers \"what's the state\" in 5 seconds.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-01-24T08:14:34.31356-08:00","created_by":"dylanconlin","updated_at":"2026-01-24T08:27:48.806789-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-24T08:27:48.806789-08:00","close_reason":"Phase: Complete - Implemented orch frontier CLI command with pkg/frontier package. Tests: go test ./pkg/frontier/... - 3 tests passed, 0 failed. Command shows ready/blocked/active issues with leverage calculation.","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"orch-go-2fut9","depends_on_id":"orch-go-9xwt8","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-24T08:14:58.53946-08:00","created_by":"dylanconlin","authority":"daemon"}]}
