{"id":"orch-go-338","title":"Fix: pkg/verify/check.go uses wrong JSON tag for comment text","description":"The Comment struct in pkg/verify/check.go uses json:\"content\" but the bd CLI returns json:\"text\". This causes orch complete to fail verification because it can't find Phase: Complete comments.","notes":"workspace: .orch/workspace/og-debug-fix-pkg-verify-3206-20dec","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2025-12-20T10:49:16.984058-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-20T10:59:48.491755-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-20T10:59:48.491755-08:00"}
