wn Command Implementation\n2025-12-19 [INV] CLI Orch Status Command\n2025-12-19 [INV] CLI Project Scaffolding and Build Setup\n2025-12-19 [INV] OpenCode Client Package Session Management\n... (run kb chronicle for full timeline)\n```\n\n### Suggested Action\n\n1. Run `kb chronicle \"synthesis\"` to understand evolution\n2. Identify patterns and contradictions across investigations\n3. Create a synthesized decision or consolidated investigation\n","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-08T11:11:03.478557-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-08T16:15:43.188187-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-08T16:15:43.188187-08:00","close_reason":"Phase: Complete - Analyzed 26 synthesis investigations, found they are meta-topic (about synthesis system, not domain knowledge). Recommended meta-topic exclusions instead of guide creation. Investigation and SYNTHESIS.md committed.","labels":["triage:review"]}
