{"id":"orch-go-3puvy","title":"Knowledge System Cleanup - Reduce Before Adding","description":"Strategic cleanup of knowledge system before adding more instrumentation. Goal: complete the synthesis loop and reduce noise so future tooling has clean data to work with.\n\n## Context\n- 629 investigations accumulating (not archived after synthesis)\n- orch patterns showing noise (sleep, generic globs)\n- kb reflect duplicating orch's synthesis detection\n- Meta-topics (investigation, synthesis) polluting suggestions\n\n## Phases\n\n### Phase 1: Reduce Noise\n- [ ] feat-043: Add meta-topic exclusions to synthesis detection\n- [ ] Fix kb reflect to align with orch (or dedupe)\n- [ ] Prune orch patterns noise\n\n### Phase 2: Complete Synthesis Loop  \n- [ ] feat-042: Implement kb archive --synthesized-into {guide}\n- [ ] Batch archive existing synthesized investigations (dashboard, spawn, daemon)\n\n### Phase 3: Instrument (post-cleanup)\n- [ ] Consider kb stats command\n- [ ] Consider read tracking for guides\n\n## Success Criteria\n- Synthesis opportunities show only actionable topics\n- Investigations archived after synthesis (count stabilizes)\n- orch patterns shows actionable signals, not noise\n- One source of truth for synthesis suggestions","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-01-07T22:40:31.897974-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-14T22:03:38.127881-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-14T22:03:38.127881-08:00","close_reason":"Phase 1 complete, future phases can be separate epics","labels":["triage:ready"]}
{"id":"orch-go-3puvy.4","title":"Add meta-topic exclusions to synthesis detection (feat-043)","description":"Quick win (~30 min): Exclude meta-topics from synthesis opportunity detection.\n\n## Problem\nTopics like 'investigation' (35 files), 'synthesis', 'artifact', 'skill' pollute synthesis suggestions. These are about the system itself, not domain topics worth synthesizing.\n\n## Solution\nUpdate pkg/verify/synthesis_opportunities.go to exclude meta-topics from TopicKeywords or add an exclusion list.\n\n## Acceptance\n- orch status no longer shows 'investigation' as synthesis opportunity\n- kb reflect (if it uses same logic) also excludes meta-topics\n\n## Context\nPart of epic orch-go-3puvy (Knowledge System Cleanup)\nArchitect design: .kb/investigations/2026-01-07-design-post-synthesis-investigation-archival.md","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-07T22:43:06.992072-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-08T13:19:03.25905-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-08T13:19:03.25905-08:00","close_reason":"Excluded meta-topics (investigation, synthesis, artifact, skill) from TopicKeywords. All tests pass. SYNTHESIS.md created.","labels":["triage:ready"]}
{"id":"orch-go-3puvy.5","title":"Fix kb reflect synthesis detection alignment","description":"Fix kb reflect to align with orch's synthesis detection (or dedupe).\n\n## Problem\nkb reflect shows 'dashboard (54 investigations)' as needing synthesis even though dashboard.md guide exists. orch status correctly excludes it. Two tools, inconsistent results.\n\n## Options\n1. Fix kb reflect to use same logic as orch (check for existing guides)\n2. Have kb reflect call orch's detection (single source of truth)\n3. Remove synthesis detection from kb reflect (let orch own it)\n\n## Acceptance\n- kb reflect and orch status show consistent synthesis opportunities\n- No duplicate/conflicting suggestions\n\n## Context\nPart of epic orch-go-3puvy (Knowledge System Cleanup)","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-07T22:43:08.648629-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-08T17:57:48.236898-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-08T17:57:48.236898-08:00","close_reason":"Fix spawned as orch-go-k63qu - adding guide existence check to kb reflect synthesis detection","labels":["triage:ready"]}
{"id":"orch-go-3puvy.6","title":"Prune orch patterns noise","description":"Filter out noise from orch patterns output.\n\n## Problem\norch patterns shows 31 'critical' patterns that aren't actionable:\n- 'Bash on *.' 354 times (pattern extraction bug)\n- 'sleep 3' empty results (expected behavior)\n- Generic globs returning empty (normal exploration)\n\n## Solution\n- Fix pattern extraction to get meaningful command summaries\n- Filter out known-benign patterns (sleep, empty globs)\n- Consider severity recalibration\n\n## Acceptance\n- orch patterns shows actionable signals\n- Critical patterns are actually critical\n- Noise reduced by \u003e80%\n\n## Context\nPart of epic orch-go-3puvy (Knowledge System Cleanup)","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-07T22:43:10.278217-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-14T22:02:52.529715-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-14T22:02:52.529715-08:00","close_reason":"87% noise reduction verified in SYNTHESIS: 23 critical patterns reduced to 3, all tests pass"}
