{"id":"orch-go-42hy","title":"Implement IsLive() function for agent liveness detection","description":"Create pkg/state/reconcile.go with IsLive(beadsID string) (tmuxLive, opencodeLive bool) that cross-references all 4 state sources (OpenCode sessions, tmux windows, beads issues, workspaces) to determine if an agent is actually running. This is the foundation for fixing phantom agents in status and adding warnings to complete. See .kb/investigations/2025-12-22-inv-audit-orchestration-lifecycle-post-registry.md","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-22T06:46:42.913015-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-22T07:08:44.041937-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-22T07:08:44.041937-08:00"}
