{"id":"orch-go-4fvlg","title":"Synthesize daemon investigations (28)","description":"## Synthesis Needed\n\nTopic **daemon** has accumulated 28 investigations that may benefit from consolidation.\n\n### Investigations to synthesize:\n\n- 2025-12-20-inv-add-dry-run-flag-daemon.md\n- 2025-12-20-inv-orch-add-daemon-command.md\n- 2025-12-21-inv-daemon-hook-integration-kb-reflect.md\n- 2025-12-22-inv-add-concurrency-control-daemon-worker.md\n- 2025-12-22-inv-phase-daemon-hook-integration-add.md\n- 2025-12-24-inv-daemon-autostart-race-condition-causing.md\n- 2025-12-24-inv-daemon-finds-triage-ready-issues.md\n- 2025-12-24-inv-daemon-selects-issues-triage-ready.md\n- 2025-12-24-inv-daemon-uses-bd-list-status.md\n- 2025-12-25-inv-add-daemon-completion-polling-close.md\n- 2025-12-25-inv-migrate-daemon-listreadyissues-use-new.md\n- 2025-12-26-debug-daemon-capacity-stale-after-complete.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-daemon-capacity-count-goes-stale.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-daemon-capacity-count-stale-after.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-daemon-capacity-count-stuck-while.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-daemon-needs-restart-after-make.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-daemon-writes-status-file-each.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-document-daemon-launchd-setup-orchestrator.md\n- 2026-01-03-inv-test-verify-daemon-skip-functionality.md\n- 2026-01-04-debug-daemon-show-rejection-reasons-preview.md\n- 2026-01-04-inv-add-hotspot-warnings-orch-daemon.md\n- 2026-01-04-inv-design-analyze-pkg-daemon-daemon.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-add-periodic-kb-reflect-daemon.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-cross-project-daemon-single-daemon.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-daemon-auto-complete-agents-report.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-daemon-blocks-child-tasks-parent.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-daemon-doesn-see-issues-newly.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-daemon-spawns-duplicate-agents-same.md\n\n### Chronicle Timeline\n\n```\n2025-12-20 [INV] Add --dry-run flag to daemon run command\n2025-12-20 [INV] Add orch review command for batch completion wo...\n2025-12-20 [INV] Add Usage/Capacity Tracking to Account Package\n2025-12-20 [INV] Add Wait Command to orch-go\n2025-12-20 [INV] Compare orch-cli (Python) vs orch-go Features\n... (run kb chronicle for full timeline)\n```\n\n### Suggested Action\n\n1. Run `kb chronicle \"daemon\"` to understand evolution\n2. Identify patterns and contradictions across investigations\n3. Create a synthesized decision or consolidated investigation\n","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-08T12:13:48.354124-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-08T14:57:34.871065-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-08T14:57:34.871065-08:00","close_reason":"Duplicate synthesis issue","labels":["triage:review"]}
{"id":"orch-go-4fwje","title":"Implement directory-based worker detection in session.created event","description":"## Problem\n\nCoaching plugin fires alerts on worker sessions because current detection (file-path based) runs too late. Detection checks tool arguments in `tool.execute.after`, but coaching alerts fire in the same hook on the first tool call - before detection has succeeded.\n\n## Solution\n\nDetect workers at session creation time using directory path. Workers spawn into `.orch/workspace/` directories - this path is known before any tool calls.\n\n## Tasks\n\n1. **Verify session.created event payload** - Log/inspect what properties are available in session.created event. Confirm `directory` is present. If not, identify how to get it (session lookup via API?)\n\n2. **Add event hook to coaching.ts** - Handle session.created, extract sessionID and directory, add to workerSessions cache if directory contains `.orch/workspace/`\n\n3. **Test all spawn modes** - Verify detection works for API headless, Claude CLI mode, and Docker spawns\n\n4. **Validate no false positives** - Ensure orchestrator sessions don't have `.orch/workspace/` in their path\n\n## Success Criteria\n\n- No coaching alerts fire on worker sessions\n- Orchestrator sessions continue receiving coaching\n- Works across all spawn paths\n\n## Reference\n\nInvestigation: `.kb/investigations/2026-01-23-inv-review-coaching-plugin-worker-detection.md`","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-01-23T18:13:58.628961-08:00","created_by":"dylanconlin","updated_at":"2026-01-23T18:19:26.427435-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-23T18:19:26.427435-08:00","close_reason":"Phase: Complete - Verified session.created event includes directory at event.properties.info.directory (required field in Session.Info schema). Implementation can proceed."}
