{"id":"orch-go-4ijfx","title":"Implement decision review triggers after N patches","description":"When investigations accumulate patches to the same area/decision, trigger reconsideration. After 3rd patch addressing issues from same decision, gate on architect review before allowing more tactical fixes. Prevents launchd-style patch accumulation.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-09T16:06:03.054688-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-10T15:17:16.660033-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-10T15:17:16.660033-08:00","close_reason":"Decision review triggers implemented with grep-based detection, warns at \u003e=1 patch, blocks at \u003e=3 patches. All tests pass, binary built and installed. Investigation and SYNTHESIS.md committed."}
