is orchestrator work per decision 2026-01-07. Opportunities now surfaced via orch status.","labels":["triage:review"]}
{"id":"orch-go-51jz","title":"Fix cross-project directory context in FallbackClose and CloseIssue","description":"Root cause from orch-go-rzch investigation:\n\n1. FallbackClose in pkg/beads/client.go:738-747 needs cmd.Dir set to DefaultDir\n2. CloseIssue in pkg/verify/check.go:570-583 needs WithCwd option on RPC client  \n3. Phase detection in orch complete also affected (can't read comments from correct beads dir)\n\nThis causes 'silent failures' when orchestrator runs orch complete - the issue appears closed but isn't.\n\nSee: .kb/investigations/2026-01-03-inv-agents-going-idle-without-phase.md","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-01-03T20:58:18.296529-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-03T21:09:55.251206-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-03T21:09:55.251206-08:00","close_reason":"Fixed all 10 Fallback functions + 10 RPC client initializations for cross-project context"}
