sized decision or consolidated investigation\n","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-08T14:24:08.929235-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-08T14:57:21.995716-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-08T14:57:21.995716-08:00","close_reason":"Duplicate synthesis issue","labels":["triage:review"]}
