{"id":"orch-go-578d","title":"orch next: Synthesize prioritized work recommendations","description":"Combine multiple signals into ranked 'what to work on next' recommendations.\n\nCurrent state: Orchestrator must manually run and synthesize:\n- bd ready (available work)\n- orch patterns (problem areas)\n- orch focus (strategic alignment)\n- orch learn (knowledge gaps)\n\nDesired state: `orch next` synthesizes these into prioritized recommendations:\n1. Critical blockers (patterns showing active failures)\n2. Focus-aligned ready work\n3. High-value maintenance (recurring patterns worth fixing)\n4. Strategic backlog\n\nExample output:\n```\norch next\n\nRECOMMENDED NEXT ACTIONS (aligned with focus: 'Ship snap MVP')\n\n1. [BLOCKER] orch-go-xyz has failed 3x in last 24h - spawn systematic-debugging\n2. [FOCUS] orch-go-abc ready - implements snap auth (P1)\n3. [FOCUS] orch-go-def ready - snap API endpoint (P2)\n4. [MAINTENANCE] 'chrome launch' gap occurred 5x - consider kn constrain\n5. [BACKLOG] orch-go-ghi ready - consolidation phase 1 (P2, not focus-aligned)\n```\n\nKey behaviors:\n- Filter patterns to active/open issues only\n- Weight by focus alignment\n- Surface blockers before new work\n- Show reasoning for prioritization","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2025-12-28T09:22:09.775647-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-29T09:18:45.967694-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-29T09:18:45.967694-08:00","close_reason":"Zombie issue reconciled - no active agent found","labels":["triage:ready"]}
{"id":"orch-go-57dn","title":"Apply pre-commit hook whitelist fix to 13 other repos with same issue","description":"The pre-commit.old hook in .git/hooks/ is local to each repo and not tracked. The same issue (blocking automation with read command) exists in: agentlog, beads-ui-svelte, beads-ui, beads, blog, glass, kb-cli, kn, opencode, orch-cli, skill-benchmark, superpowers. Apply same fix: KEYWORD_EXEMPT_DIRS whitelist + is_batch_mode() detection. See .kb/investigations/2026-01-03-inv-debug-pre-commit-hook-interactive-enter.md","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-03T20:18:11.353872-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-03T20:48:09.067012-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-03T20:48:09.067012-08:00","close_reason":"Investigation complete - git hooks local-only","labels":["triage:review"]}
