{"id":"orch-go-5slj","title":"Enhance orch handoff with D.E.K.N. scaffold and gate","description":"Current handoff generates metadata but misses the valuable synthesis. Hybrid approach: auto-generate scaffold with data (completions, git state, beads), add D.E.K.N. sections with prompts, gate on non-empty synthesis before saving to file. See skillc/.orch/SESSION_HANDOFF.md for reference of good manual handoff.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-24T07:19:59.406672-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T22:30:16.87865-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-25T22:30:16.87865-08:00","close_reason":"Enhanced orch handoff with hybrid D.E.K.N. scaffold: auto-populated data (Delta from completions, Evidence from git stats 69 commits +51499/-3050 lines) + synthesis prompts (Knowledge, Next require human input). All 22 tests pass."}
