{"id":"orch-go-5y93","title":"Dashboard: add search/filter for agent archive","description":"With 477 agents in archive, finding a specific agent is difficult. Add search box that filters by workspace name, beads ID, task description, or skill type.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2025-12-27T19:02:32.086463-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-27T19:13:08.861249-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-27T19:13:08.861249-08:00","close_reason":"Added search input to dashboard filter bar. Searches across workspace name, beads ID, task, title, skill, and project. Case-insensitive, integrates with existing filter chain. Build passes, committed.","labels":["triage:ready"]}
{"id":"orch-go-5yec","title":"Add orch init command for project scaffolding","description":"From inv-scope-orch-init investigation:\n\n**Problem:** New projects need manual setup of .beads/, .kb/, .orch/, CLAUDE.md. Inconsistent across repos.\n\n**Solution:** `orch init` command that:\n1. Creates directory structure (.beads/, .kb/investigations/, .orch/workspace/, .orch/templates/)\n2. Copies SYNTHESIS.md template\n3. Creates minimal CLAUDE.md if missing\n4. Runs `bd init` if beads not initialized\n5. Adds to ~/.orch/projects.yaml for cross-project tracking\n\n**Flags:**\n- `--minimal` - just directories, no templates\n- `--force` - overwrite existing\n\n**Also includes:**\n- Port allocation registry integration\n- Tmuxinator config generation\n\nRef: .kb/investigations/2025-12-21-inv-scope-orch-init-project-standardization.md","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-21T23:27:49.596739-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-21T23:39:42.452814-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-21T23:39:42.452814-08:00"}
