{"id":"orch-go-6xya","title":"Dashboard Active section not showing daemon-spawned agents","description":"orch status shows 3 active agents but dashboard Active section shows only 1. The daemon-spawned agents (orch-go-7nmw, orch-go-d1s5) appear in Agent Lifecycle events as daemon.spawn but don't show in Active grid. Likely filtering or status detection issue for daemon-spawned sessions.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-26T09:26:20.275059-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-26T09:40:03.810342-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-26T09:40:03.810342-08:00","close_reason":"Fixed dashboard Active section by preventing Phase: Complete and SYNTHESIS.md from overriding active OpenCode session status. Commit a4dfcff3.","labels":["P1","skill:systematic-debugging","triage:ready"]}
{"id":"orch-go-6yeb","title":"Agents not reporting test evidence in beads comments","description":"Agents claim 'tests pass' but don't include actual test output in beads comments. This triggers the test evidence gate in orch complete, forcing use of --force.\n\n## Root cause\nSkills don't enforce test output format in comments. Agent says 'All tests pass' without running bd comment with actual output.\n\n## Solution\nUpdate skill phases to require: bd comment \u003cid\u003e 'Tests: \u003ccommand\u003e - \u003cactual output summary\u003e'","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-01-04T08:37:33.048723-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-04T08:50:20.93588-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-04T08:50:20.93588-08:00","close_reason":"Updated 6 skill files to require actual test output format: 'Tests: \u003ccommand\u003e - \u003cactual output\u003e'. Deployed via skillc. Commit: 60b9ad6"}
{"id":"orch-go-6z1nf","title":"Synthesize extract investigations (13)","description":"## Synthesis Needed\n\nTopic **extract** has accumulated 13 investigations that may benefit from consolidation.\n\n### Investigations to synthesize:\n\n- 2026-01-03-inv-extract-serve-agents-go-serve.md\n- 2026-01-03-inv-extract-serve-learn-go-serve.md\n- 2026-01-03-inv-extract-serve-system-go-serve.md\n- 2026-01-03-inv-extract-shared-go-utility-functions.md\n- 2026-01-03-inv-extract-status-cmd-go-main.md\n- 2026-01-04-inv-extract-clean-cmd-go-main.md\n- 2026-01-04-inv-extract-small-commands-send-tail.md\n- 2026-01-04-inv-phase-extract-serve-agents-cache.md\n- 2026-01-04-inv-phase-extract-serve-agents-events.md\n- 2026-01-04-inv-phase-extract-statsbar-component-extract.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-extract-activitytab-component-part-orch.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-extract-synthesistab-component-part-orch.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-implement-kb-extract-command-cross.md\n\n### Chronicle Timeline\n\n```\n2025-12-19 [INV] OpenCode Client Package Session Management\n2025-12-19 [INV] SSE Event Monitoring Client\n2025-12-19 [INV] Desktop Notifications on Completion\n2025-12-19 [INV] Fix SSE parsing - event type inside JSON data\n2025-12-19 [INV] OpenCode POC - Spawn Session Via Go\n... (run kb chronicle for full timeline)\n```\n\n### Suggested Action\n\n1. Run `kb chronicle \"extract\"` to understand evolution\n2. Identify patterns and contradictions across investigations\n3. Create a synthesized decision or consolidated investigation\n","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-07T22:39:38.805471-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-07T22:46:44.588146-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-07T22:46:44.588146-08:00","close_reason":"Bulk close: kb reflect synthesis issues are noise until detection is fixed","labels":["triage:review"]}
