ction.md\n- 2026-01-05-inv-update-meta-orchestrator-skill-session.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-detect-orchestrator-frame-collapse-doing.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-diagnose-orchestrator-skill-18-completion.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-interactive-orchestrator-sessions-don-create.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-orchestrator-sessions-checkpoint-discipline-max.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-orchestrator-sessions-spawned-via-tmux.md\n- 2026-01-07-design-orch-stats-miscounts-orchestrator-meta.md\n\n### Chronicle Timeline\n\n```\n2025-12-19 [INV] CLI orch complete Command Implementation\n2025-12-19 [INV] CLI orch spawn Command Implementation\n2025-12-19 [INV] Set beads issue status to in_progress on spawn\n2025-12-20 [INV] Explore Tradeoffs for orch-go OpenCode Integration\n2025-12-20 [INV] Synthesis Protocol Design for Agent Handoffs\n... (run kb chronicle for full timeline)\n```\n\n### Suggested Action\n\n1. Run `kb chronicle \"orchestrator\"` to understand evolution\n2. Identify patterns and contradictions across investigations\n3. Create a synthesized decision or consolidated investigation\n","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-07T08:21:32.976205-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-07T11:40:53.281066-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-07T11:40:53.281066-08:00","close_reason":"Bulk close: synthesis issues disabled","labels":["triage:review"]}
