{"id":"orch-go-77zk","title":"Implement progressive disclosure in swarm dashboard","description":"Dashboard shows 185 agents in flat grid - overwhelming. Per investigation 2025-12-23-inv-design-question-should-swarm-dashboard.md, implement collapsible sections: Active (expanded by default), Recent (collapsed, \u003c24h), Archive (collapsed, \u003e24h). Store collapse state in localStorage. Show counts in section headers.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-24T08:01:40.823244-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-24T08:20:40.526419-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-24T08:20:40.526419-08:00","close_reason":"Implemented progressive disclosure with collapsible Active/Recent/Archive sections, localStorage persistence for section state, and updated stats bar. All tests pass (18/19, 1 pre-existing API dependency issue).","labels":["triage:ready"]}
