{"id":"orch-go-7k9y","title":"orch learn act: suggested commands have TODO placeholders that fail kn's 20-char minimum","description":"When orch learn act runs the suggested command, it uses placeholders like '--reason \"TODO: document constraint\"' which fail kn's validation (requires 20+ chars). Either: 1) Generate better default reasons from the gap context, 2) Prompt user for reason interactively, 3) Allow marking suggestion as 'addressed' without running exact command.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-25T20:28:07.579315-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T20:37:15.029392-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-25T20:37:15.029392-08:00","close_reason":"Fixed orch learn act: generates real reasons from gap context (skills, tasks, occurrence counts). Added orch learn resolve for manual resolution. 27 tests pass.","labels":["skill:feature-impl","triage:ready"]}
