hboard-api-returns-null-beadsid.md\n- 2026-01-04-inv-design-analyze-dashboard-ui-structure.md\n- 2026-01-05-design-review-dashboard-architecture-request-handling.md\n- 2026-01-05-inv-dashboard-connection-pool-exhaustion-sse.md\n- 2026-01-05-inv-dashboard-visibility-orchestrator-sessions-orch.md\n- 2026-01-05-inv-fix-dashboard-connection-pool-exhaustion.md\n- 2026-01-05-inv-fix-dashboard-excessive-agents-fetch.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-dashboard-api-slow-again-623.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-dashboard-long-outcome-text-overflows.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-dashboard-playwright-tests-run-headless.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-orch-go-hmj61-dashboard-agent.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-add-pending-reviews-section-dashboard.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-dashboard-move-ready-queue-dedicated.md\n\n### Chronicle Timeline\n\n```\n2025-12-20 [INV] Legacy Artifacts Synthesis Protocol Alignment\n2025-12-20 [INV] Add /api/agentlog endpoint to serve.go\n2025-12-20 [INV] Add Usage/Capacity Tracking to Account Package\n2025-12-20 [INV] Implement Synthesis Card Display in Swarm Dashb...\n2025-12-20 [INV] Scaffold beads-ui v2 (Bun + SvelteKit 5 + shadc...\n... (run kb chronicle for full timeline)\n```\n\n### Suggested Action\n\n1. Run `kb chronicle \"dashboard\"` to understand evolution\n2. Identify patterns and contradictions across investigations\n3. Create a synthesized decision or consolidated investigation\n","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-06T19:36:04.730716-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-06T22:02:36.611341-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-06T22:02:36.611341-08:00","close_reason":"Duplicate - keeping newest issue per topic","labels":["triage:review"]}
{"id":"orch-go-7uxz","title":"[orch-go] feature-impl: Fix ~3s hydration delay on Swarm Dashboard. Pro...","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-27T09:21:13.782378-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-27T09:28:45.307546-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-27T09:28:45.307546-08:00","close_reason":"Fixed ~3s hydration delay by implementing tiered fetch priority: critical data (agents via SSE, beads, pendingReviews) loads immediately, secondary data (usage, focus, servers, daemon) deferred to requestIdleCallback. Leave it Better: recorded kn decision on requestIdleCallback pattern."}
