{"id":"orch-go-7z6r","title":"orch complete: prompt for follow-up issues from investigation recommendations","description":"Finish ok-je0: When completing an investigation, parse SYNTHESIS.md NextActions and prompt orchestrator to create beads issues for implementation recommendations. Currently parses and displays but doesn't prompt for action. Pattern: 'Investigation recommends implementation. Create follow-up issue? [y/N]'","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2025-12-24T10:49:33.396015-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T13:57:40.556475-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-25T13:57:40.556475-08:00","close_reason":"Enhanced orch complete to prompt for each SYNTHESIS.md recommendation individually and create beads issues directly with [y/N/q] interaction","labels":["skill:feature-impl","triage:ready"]}
{"id":"orch-go-7zhqm","title":"orch complete triggers handoff section updates","description":"Part of progressive session capture (decision 2026-01-14). When orch complete runs, prompt to update handoff sections: 1) Spawns table - add outcome for completed agent, 2) Evidence - what was observed, 3) Knowledge - decisions made. Read current handoff, prompt for updates, write back. Location: cmd/orch/complete.go or session.go","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-14T13:25:38.676345-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-14T18:21:57.903359-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-14T18:21:57.903359-08:00","close_reason":"Progressive session capture features implemented: session start prompts, complete triggers, and validate command all working","labels":["triage:ready"]}
