{"id":"orch-go-80tq","title":"Skip test evidence gate for markdown-only changes","description":"Test evidence gate (pkg/verify/test_evidence.go) blocks completion when code files modified without test output. Currently triggers on ANY file changes. Should detect markdown-only changes (.md files) and skip the gate - no tests exist for documentation/template changes. Discovered when completing orch-go-mgtw (template headers) required --force.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-30T07:23:27.825583-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-03T20:45:46.065351-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-03T20:45:46.065351-08:00","close_reason":"Already fixed in e249dfe8 - HasCodeChangesSinceSpawn uses spawn time"}
