{"id":"orch-go-8jgxw","title":"Build model-advisor tool with live API data","description":"Investigate available APIs for model comparison data (Artificial Analysis, OpenRouter, etc.) and build a tool that answers 'which model for this task at this budget?' on demand. Should track: pricing, latency, quality scores, tool-use accuracy. Consider logging our own spawn performance data as ground truth. Goal: stop manually researching model options every time costs/limits change.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-09T12:32:25.122633-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-17T10:41:14.440656-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-17T10:41:14.440656-08:00","close_reason":"Model-advisor tool delivered with OpenRouter API client, CLI commands (list/recommend/cache), 24h caching, and task-specific scoring. Tested and committed.","labels":["triage:ready"]}
