{"id":"orch-go-8khw","title":"Create pkg/beads abstraction layer (Phase 3)","description":"## Context\n\nEcosystem audit follow-up (orch-go-tyvz, orch-go-cnq5) confirmed beads should remain as external dependency with abstraction layer to isolate API changes and enable testing.\n\n## Current State\n\n- 19 exec.Command calls across orch-go using 7 bd commands\n- Direct CLI calls scattered in daemon, verify, serve, spawn packages\n- No mock testing possible for beads interactions\n\n## Implementation\n\n### 1. pkg/beads/interface.go\nDefine interface for the 7 commands used:\n- `Comment(issueID, text string)` - Add progress comment\n- `Comments(issueID string)` - Get comments\n- `Create(title, desc string, opts CreateOpts)` - Create issue\n- `List(opts ListOpts)` - Query issues\n- `Ready()` - Get ready queue\n- `Show(issueID string)` - Get issue details\n- `Stats()` - Dashboard stats\n\n### 2. pkg/beads/client.go\nImplement interface via bd CLI exec.Command calls.\n\n### 3. pkg/beads/mock.go\nMock implementation for unit testing.\n\n### 4. Migrate consumers\n- pkg/daemon/ - Ready queue polling\n- pkg/verify/ - Comment and issue checks\n- cmd/orch/serve.go - Stats API\n- pkg/spawn/ - Issue context loading\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] Zero direct exec.Command(\"bd\", ...) calls outside pkg/beads\n- [ ] daemon package has mock-based tests\n- [ ] verify package has mock-based tests\n- [ ] All existing functionality preserved\n\n## References\n\n- .kb/investigations/2025-12-24-inv-follow-up-ecosystem-audit-orch.md\n- .kb/investigations/2025-12-24-inv-addendum-ecosystem-audit-opencode.md","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2025-12-24T17:41:43.900534-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-27T22:43:41.591399-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-27T22:43:41.591399-08:00","close_reason":"pkg/beads abstraction layer implemented - backend refactor, no UI changes","labels":["triage:ready"]}
{"id":"orch-go-8mrk","title":"orch review times out due to O(n) beads API calls","description":"Root cause: getCompletionsForReview() scans 682 workspaces, and for each of 326 with SYNTHESIS.md, calls VerifyCompletionFull -\u003e VerifyPhaseGatesForCompletion -\u003e GetComments(beadsID). Each call hits beads RPC/CLI individually.\n\nFix: Use existing GetCommentsBatch() function. Collect all beads IDs first, make one batched call, then verify with cached results.\n\nFiles involved:\n- cmd/orch/review.go:203 (calls VerifyCompletionFull per workspace)\n- pkg/verify/phase_gates.go:179 (calls GetComments individually)\n- pkg/verify/beads_api.go:432 (GetCommentsBatch exists but unused by review)","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-01-04T21:37:04.920297-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-05T09:49:32.754672-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-05T09:49:32.754672-08:00","close_reason":"Zombie issue - agent died without completing. Work started but agent lost context. Will respawn to complete.","labels":["triage:ready"]}
