{"id":"orch-go-8s2kl","title":"Epic: Dashboard API Performance - fix slow endpoints","description":"Fix slow dashboard API endpoints identified in Jan 7 performance investigation.\n\n## Context\nDashboard was taking 30+ seconds to load. Investigation found multiple slow endpoints:\n- /api/agents: 32s → fixed (627ms) \n- /api/beads: 6.5s → in progress\n- /api/beads/ready: 5.2s → in progress\n\n## Root Cause Pattern\nO(n²) complexity from nested loops + threshold regression from earlier refactor.\n\n## Reference\n- .kb/investigations/2026-01-07-inv-dashboard-api-agents-performance-synthesis.md\n\n## Success Criteria\n- All dashboard API endpoints respond in \u003c1s\n- No O(n²) patterns in endpoint handlers","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-01-07T10:40:08.999292-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-14T14:13:43.281052-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-14T14:13:43.281052-08:00","close_reason":"All children completed"}
