hboard-api-returns-null-beadsid.md\n- 2026-01-04-inv-design-analyze-dashboard-ui-structure.md\n- 2026-01-05-design-review-dashboard-architecture-request-handling.md\n- 2026-01-05-inv-dashboard-connection-pool-exhaustion-sse.md\n- 2026-01-05-inv-dashboard-visibility-orchestrator-sessions-orch.md\n- 2026-01-05-inv-fix-dashboard-connection-pool-exhaustion.md\n- 2026-01-05-inv-fix-dashboard-excessive-agents-fetch.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-add-pending-reviews-section-dashboard.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-dashboard-move-ready-queue-dedicated.md\n\n### Chronicle Timeline\n\n```\n2025-12-20 [INV] Legacy Artifacts Synthesis Protocol Alignment\n2025-12-20 [INV] Add /api/agentlog endpoint to serve.go\n2025-12-20 [INV] Add Usage/Capacity Tracking to Account Package\n2025-12-20 [INV] Implement Synthesis Card Display in Swarm Dashb...\n2025-12-20 [INV] Scaffold beads-ui v2 (Bun + SvelteKit 5 + shadc...\n... (run kb chronicle for full timeline)\n```\n\n### Suggested Action\n\n1. Run `kb chronicle \"dashboard\"` to understand evolution\n2. Identify patterns and contradictions across investigations\n3. Run `kb create guide \"dashboard\"` to create authoritative reference\n","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-06T12:18:54.725935-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-06T18:04:22.180533-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-06T18:04:22.180533-08:00","close_reason":"Dashboard guide synthesis - no code changes, documentation only"}
