{"id":"orch-go-928i","title":"Port full OpenCode theme system with named themes","description":"orch-go-t84l was closed with only Light/Dark/System toggle, but the original request was to port OpenCode's full theme system. Still needed: 1) Create lib/themes/ with CSS variables per theme, 2) Add named themes: dracula, nord, tokyonight, catppuccin, one-dark, gruvbox, github, opencode, 3) Update theme store to support named themes, 4) Update dropdown to show all theme options. Reference: .kb/investigations/2025-12-26-inv-opencode-theme-selection-system.md","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2025-12-26T22:06:56.02585-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-26T22:34:13.32161-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-26T22:34:13.32161-08:00","close_reason":"Ported full OpenCode theme system with 28 named themes, TypeScript types, resolution logic, CSS variable generation, and updated ThemeToggle component. Commit: d4a08dc3","labels":["skill:feature-impl","triage:ready"]}
