{"id":"orch-go-957w","title":"Implement SpawnTelemetry for observability MVP","description":"Add SpawnTelemetry event to events.jsonl at spawn time. Captures: context_size_chars, context_size_tokens_est, kb_context stats (match_count, was_truncated, constraints/decisions/investigations counts), behavioral_patterns_count, skill, tier. ~200 lines in pkg/spawn/. See investigation: .kb/investigations/2025-12-30-inv-design-observability-infrastructure-validating-principle.md","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2025-12-30T08:39:56.084477-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-30T09:18:52.507291-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-30T09:18:52.507291-08:00","close_reason":"Implemented SpawnTelemetry event type with 7 tests. Telemetry logged to events.jsonl at spawn time with context size, token estimates, and kb context stats via GapAnalysis fallback."}
