{"id":"orch-go-9u685","title":"orch status: Surface synthesis opportunities","description":"Add synthesis opportunity surfacing to orch status.\n\n## Context\nStrategic Orchestrator Model - orchestrator comprehends, which includes knowing when synthesis is needed.\n\n## Logic\nQuery .kb/investigations/ for completed investigations. Group by topic keywords. If 3+ investigations share topic and no corresponding Guide or Decision exists → surface.\n\n## Threshold\nFrom Coherence Over Patches principle: '3+ investigations on topic without Guide signals needs synthesis'\n\n## Output format\n```\nSYNTHESIS OPPORTUNITIES\n  3 investigations on 'daemon' without synthesis\n  4 investigations on 'dashboard' without synthesis\n```\n\n## Location\norch-go (orch status command)\n\n## Validation\n- orch status shows synthesis opportunities section when threshold met\n- Section hidden when no opportunities exist","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-01-07T14:08:08.675165-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-07T14:41:11.658905-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-07T14:41:11.658905-08:00","close_reason":"Added synthesis opportunity surfacing to orch status. When 3+ investigations share a topic without a corresponding Guide or Decision, the status output displays a SYNTHESIS OPPORTUNITIES section. Implemented via pkg/verify/synthesis_opportunities.go with 8 tests."}
