{"id":"orch-go-abeu","title":"Update orch-knowledge source templates with structured uncertainty","description":"Agent og-feat-update-investigation-templates-22dec updated ~/.claude/skills/ (deployed) but NOT /Users/dylanconlin/orch-knowledge/skills/src/ (source). Next 'orch build skills' will overwrite the changes.\n\nNeed to apply same changes to source:\n- Remove 'Confidence: X%' line from D.E.K.N.\n- Rename 'What's certain' → 'What's tested'\n- Rename 'What's uncertain' → 'What's untested'  \n- Add 'What would change this' section\n\nFiles in orch-knowledge/skills/src/worker/:\n- investigation/SKILL.md\n- investigation/templates/investigation.md\n- research/SKILL.md\n- research/templates/research.md\n- feature-impl/src/phases/investigation.md\n- reliability-testing/SKILL.md\n\nSee decision: .kb/decisions/2025-12-22-replace-confidence-scores-with-structured-uncertainty.md","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-22T07:48:03.774558-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-27T19:03:43.574196-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-27T19:03:43.574196-08:00","close_reason":"Updated orch-knowledge source templates with structured uncertainty pattern. Changed research skill source (.skillc/SKILL.md.template, skill.yaml) and template file to replace confidence percentages with tested/untested/would-change sections. Investigation skill already had correct D.E.K.N. format. Feature-impl investigation phase already had updated language.","labels":["triage:ready"]}
{"id":"orch-go-abyae","title":"Synthesize opencode investigations (19)","description":"## Synthesis Needed\n\nTopic **opencode** has accumulated 19 investigations that may benefit from consolidation.\n\n### Investigations to synthesize:\n\n- 2025-12-19-inv-client-opencode-session-management.md\n- 2025-12-19-simple-opencode-poc-spawn-session-via.md\n- 2025-12-20-design-explore-tradeoffs-orch-opencode-integration.md\n- 2025-12-20-inv-refactor-orch-tail-use-opencode.md\n- 2025-12-20-research-opencode-native-context-loading.md\n- 2025-12-21-inv-implement-verify-opencode-disk-session.md\n- 2025-12-23-debug-opencode-api-redirect-loop.md\n- 2025-12-23-inv-oc-command-opencode-dev-wrapper.md\n- 2025-12-24-inv-addendum-ecosystem-audit-opencode.md\n- 2025-12-24-inv-fix-orch-clean-verify-opencode.md\n- 2025-12-25-inv-opencode-crashes-no-user-message.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-can-we-auto-refresh-opencode.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-investigate-opencode-session-accumulation-causing.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-opencode-health-endpoint-returns-redirected.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-opencode-theme-selection-system.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-port-full-opencode-theme-system.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-cannot-query-opencode-sessions-other.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-implement-opencode-session-cleanup-mechanism.md\n- 2026-01-07-inv-update-core-skills-opencode-ask.md\n\n### Chronicle Timeline\n\n```\n2025-12-19 [INV] CLI orch spawn Command Implementation\n2025-12-19 [INV] CLI Orch Status Command\n2025-12-19 [INV] CLI Project Scaffolding and Build Setup\n2025-12-19 [INV] OpenCode Client Package Session Management\n2025-12-19 [INV] SSE Event Monitoring Client\n... (run kb chronicle for full timeline)\n```\n\n### Suggested Action\n\n1. Run `kb chronicle \"opencode\"` to understand evolution\n2. Identify patterns and contradictions across investigations\n3. Create a synthesized decision or consolidated investigation\n","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-07T21:14:36.2717-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-