{"id":"orch-go-afsz","title":"Dashboard: Move ready queue to dedicated section below stats bar","description":"Implement Up Next section for ready queue visibility. Design complete in .kb/investigations/2025-12-26-design-how-better-surface-ready-queue.md. Key features: 1) Dedicated CollapsibleSection below stats bar (like Pending Reviews), 2) Shows top 5 priority items sorted by P-level, 3) Auto-expands when P0/P1 items exist, 4) Each item shows: priority badge, title, age, labels, 5) Focus-aligned items get star indicator, 6) Collapse state persists in localStorage. Create UpNextSection component following Pending Reviews pattern.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-26T15:36:03.581438-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-27T14:10:28.599223-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-27T14:10:28.599223-08:00","close_reason":"Added Up Next section to dashboard showing top 5 priority items sorted by P-level. Features: priority badges with color coding, focus-aligned star indicator, auto-expand on P0/P1, localStorage persistence for collapse state, age indicators, and '+N more in queue' link. Commit: 5caf26a3. Leave it Better: kn-9a611e","labels":["skill:feature-impl","triage:ready"]}
