{"id":"orch-go-asep","title":"Add stale bug check before spawning - warn if bug may already be fixed","description":"Before spawning a bug issue, check git history for commits mentioning the issue ID or related keywords since issue creation. Warn if potentially stale. Prevents wasting agent time on already-fixed bugs (happened 5+ times with gxwu). See .kb/investigations/2025-12-30-inv-investigate-went-wrong-session-dec.md Finding 2.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2025-12-30T17:46:34.643358-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-02T10:20:40.031498-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-02T10:20:40.031498-08:00","close_reason":"Feature complete and committed - stale bug check working (verified by spawn blocking in this session)"}
