{"id":"orch-go-awfr","title":"orch status: exclude agents with closed beads issues from active count","description":"orch status shows skillc-mmq as 'idle' even though the beads issue is closed. Should check if beads issue is closed and exclude from active display, or show as 'completed'. Currently status is based only on OpenCode session activity, not beads issue state.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2025-12-24T10:58:37.517271-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T13:49:53.681903-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-25T13:49:53.681903-08:00","close_reason":"Fixed orch status to exclude agents with closed beads issues from active count. Agents with closed issues now show as 'completed' status (visible with --all flag). Changed from ListOpenIssues to GetIssuesBatch for checking closed status."}
