{"id":"orch-go-bgei","title":"orch complete/abandon fails to parse child beads IDs (dot notation)","description":"When beads ID contains a dot (e.g., orch-go-re8n.2 for epic children), orch complete and orch abandon fail with: 'json: cannot unmarshal array into Go value of type beads.Issue'. The bd show output for children includes array fields that the current parser doesn't handle. Workaround: use bd close directly.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-25T19:53:11.648-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T22:14:43.647906-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-25T22:14:43.647906-08:00","close_reason":"Batch close from orch review","labels":["skill:systematic-debugging","triage:ready"]}
